Class JovaErrorFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.tugraz.ist.cc.error.JovaErrorFactory
  • public class JovaErrorFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    A factory class to generate JovaError subclass instances with the respective error messages defined in the assignment description.
